thread.title: Millie Swann

author: Millie Swann
title: Millie Swann
text:
We really enjoy our office at 710 Collins St Docklands. This is just 250m from southern cross station & its a vibrant & busy area.
The office has fantastic view out every area & its secure & safe & the other clients working here are friendly.
My clients find its very easy & the support staff here are fantastic with them. They make my business that much more professional as I am high end consultant & the clients require a bit of extra care.
The onsite manager & support staff are first class & making comeing to my office just that much more enjoyable.
I couldnt recommend Docklands 710 office enough.
Kind regards Millie Swann on the web at millieswann.com.au
